room_title: Escape room "Road Trip " by Escape109 in Charlotte
room_description: Your infamous family vacations and the over-the-top stories that come from them have people around town calling you the Griswolds. Nothing ever seems to go as planned, but this year things have to go right! It is your job to get Grandma to her favorite vacation spot where the whole family is waiting to surprise her for her 100th birthday. But before things even get started there is already a problem, we have lost the keys, and if we don't find them within the hour we are going to ruin the surprise. Hurry, we don't have much time!
